text: You are a great friend and a good influence. As you have pointed out earlier several times that you profess a forceful espousal of opinions, I knew it well to filter some of the good ones, until this vigilance was not needed at all. Among all the good times I regard the 4th sem the best and particularly those TA202 labs. Mahesh the builder!!! C220 labs with all the jokes and 'shayaris' remain still a great memory. Our secret mission with the 'one who must not be named' must have a special place in our memories. Looking forward to good times ahead and really fruitful discussions among great jokes and 'shayaris'.
author: Md Saquib Hussain
